Please indicate if you have some level of experience with any of the following types of marketing activities:

Digital Marketing
By digital marketing, we mean the actions taken to drive marketing messages and experiences across digital channels and devices. This includes content creation, brand messaging, audience identification, data analysis, and campaign management.

Marketing Campaign ManagementBy cross-channel campaign management we mean activities that allow you to organize, design, execute, and measure marketing campaigns more effectively across different customer touch points.

Social Media Marketing
By social media marketing, we mean a variety of activities including social listening, content publishing, support, and campaign measurement, which are designed to drive specific marketing and engagement goals within your organization.

Media OptimizationBy media optimization we mean activities that allow you to get a consolidated view of how your media is performing, and the use of tools to both accurately forecast and continually optimize your media mix.

Digital Advertising Content Experience Management
By content management we managing activities related to creating and updating content in digital advertising and/or managing user created content.
